1. npm install express, mongodb, react
2. npm install devdependencies nodemon,babel,webpack "--save-dev"
3.create babelrc file and set up babel for this project
4.create webpack.config.client.js and webpack.config.server.js and webpack.config.client.production.js files
5.setup config in webpack client file
6.setip config in webpack server file
7.setip config in webpack CLIENT production file
